vote.title: An ordinance amending Chapter 51A, “Dallas Development Code: Ordinance No. 19455, as amended,” of the Dallas City Code by amending Section 51A-11.401; “Sunset Provision”; (1) providing a new sunset date; (2) providing a penalty not to exceed $2,000.00; (3) providing a saving clause; (4) providing a severability clause; and (5) providing an effect date - Estimated Revenue Foregone: General Fund ($4,019,087.00) and Debit Service Fund ($1,512,775.00), both over a five-year period
